egory:Naval battles involving Russia]]\n[[Category:Revolutions in the Russian Empire]]\n[[Category:Rebellions against the Russian Empire]]\n", "name_user": "Bebgsurg", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eOctober Manifesto", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1905_Russian_Revolution"}
